An escrow-like service that allowed safer payment by securely holding a buyer's coins in escrow until the terms of the sale are met. 

##History

The site was launched on June 23rd, 2011 (2.1).

The site launched two transaction options on June 28rd, 2011.

Service from BTCrow became inaccessible in March, 2012.

